Economic Regulator (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order 2014

I make the following order under section 36 of the Economic Regulator Act 2009 .

10 September 2014

Marinus Theodoor (Rene) Hidding

Minister for Infrastructure

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Economic Regulator (MAIB Premiums) Amendment Order 2014 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect 61 days after the day on which its making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Order
    In this order, the Economic Regulator (MAIB Premiums) Order 2013 is referred to as the Principal Order.

4.
    The amendments effected by this clause have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Economic Regulator (MAIB Premiums) Order 2013 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 17 September 2014

This order is administered by the Motor Accidents Insurance Board.
